ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to support implementation of the legislative amendments contained in the Faster Removal of Foreign Criminals Act to enhance the safety and security of Canadians, strengthen the integrity of the immigration program, and facilitate entry to support Canadian interests.
